    </custodhist>
    <processinfo id="aspace_0cb444c61aece956b36800c024f6ad00">
      <head>Processing Information</head>
      <p>General processing procedures included removing fragile newspaper clippings from cardboard scrapbook mounts and photocopying them onto acid-free paper.</p>
    </processinfo>
    <scopecontent id="aspace_b7b8d88a033c254af19c89775c37375c">
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
      <p>The contents of this collection include: correspondence, flyers, memorabilia, newsletters, newspaper clippings, poems, and songs.</p>
